  If R  \rightarrowtail  A_{1}, \ldots ,A_{n} is a relation symbol and t_{1}, \ldots ,t_{n} are terms of appropriate sorts, then { \mathopen {} \llbracket \Gamma .R(t_{1}, \ldots ,t_{n}) \rrbracket \mathclose {}} _{ M } is the following pullback:





